commands.name: play
commands.desc:
Plays a song from YouTube/SoundCloud and more.
-Full list here:https://ytdl-org.github.io/youtube-dl/supportedsites.html

commands.name: queue
commands.desc: Add song to queue. Use /play without arguments to play queue
commands.usage: queue <url> /queue to view queue /queue clear or -c to clear queue

commands.name: volume
commands.desc: Sets internal playback volume for bot. Applied when next song played

commands.name: pause
commands.desc: Pauses currently playing music. /resume to resume

commands.name: resume
commands.desc: Resumes currently paused music

commands.name: stop
commands.desc: Stops currently playing music, and clears queue

commands.name: skip
commands.desc: Skips currently playing music

commands.name: join
commands.desc: Connects bot to voice channel user is in

commands.name: jpeg
commands.desc: More jpegs an image from url or previous message
commands.usage: jpeg <url> or jpeg (will grab previous image)

commands.name: deepfry
commands.desc: Deep fries an image from url or previous message
commands.usage: deepfry <urL> or deepfry (will grab previous image)

commands.name: leave
commands.desc: Disconnects bot from voice channel

commands.name: diceroll
commands.desc: Rolls a die

commands.name: clear
commands.desc: Clears # of messages from screen. (Default 5)

commands.name: coinflip
commands.desc: Flips a coin

commands.name: gelbooru
commands.desc: Scrapes gelbooru.com for images

commands.name: haiku
commands.desc: Generates a random haiku.

commands.name: help
commands.desc: Displays list of commands.

commands.name: info
commands.desc: Displays bot info.

commands.name: insult
commands.desc: Insults a user with a random shakespearian insult.

commands.name: hentaihaven
commands.desc: Scrapes HentaiHaven.org for videos based on categories.

commands.name: lolicon
commands.desc: Exposes a user as lolicon and sends them an informational video.

commands.name: pat
commands.desc: Pats a user on the head.

commands.name: ping
commands.desc: Pings a user on the server.

commands.name: police
commands.desc: Calls the police on a user.

commands.name: pornhub
commands.desc: Scrapes PornHub.com for videos based on keywords.

commands.name: prefix
commands.desc: Sets command prefix.

commands.name: purge
commands.desc: deletes the previous few messages

commands.name: rule34
commands.desc: Scrapes rule34 for lewd images.

commands.name: spank
commands.desc: Spanks a user on the server.

commands.name: register_role
commands.desc: Registers new role for permissions

commands.name: register_channel
commands.desc: Registers new channel for permissions
